            <lg xml:id="TK832">
<l>pētaimaiyu ḷellām pētaimai kātaṉmai</l>
<l>kaiyalla taṉkaṭ ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The greatest folly is that which leads one to take delight in doing what is forbidden.</l>
            </lg>
